race.comment: MEPUNGA TULLY (8) could not have been more impressive last start in her scintillating 29.48 win at Cannington over 520m. Smart win latest and looks a key chance again here. SHARAPOVA STAR (4) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (21.67) last time out at Shepparton. Form here is sound including two wins. Leading player again. JETSTREAM ICON (7) produced a modest effort most recently when eighth at The Meadows over 525m behind Paw Ultra (31.06) in a Grade 4/5. Has never missed the frame from six starts from this draw, including two wins. Should be thereabouts. SHORTY BOY (2) warrants respect although new to this track.
